understand the truth about me.

541
00:20:43,117 --> 00:20:45,870
And so, I...

542
00:20:45,870 --> 00:20:48,789
♪

543
00:20:48,789 --> 00:20:50,624
Silly girl!

544
00:20:50,624 --> 00:20:53,252
You forced yourself to
come all the way out here.

545
00:20:53,252 --> 00:20:55,629
Please don't worry about me.

546
00:20:55,629 --> 00:20:59,049
Just as long as
you're well and happy.

547
00:20:59,049 --> 00:21:02,178
I'm so glad.

548
00:21:02,178 --> 00:21:04,054
Auntie!

549
00:21:04,054 --> 00:21:08,225
A...a good woman
shouldn't cry so easily.

550
00:21:08,225 --> 00:21:10,603
Isn't that right, Auntie?

551
00:21:10,603 --> 00:21:14,273
'Cause those tears
are much more beautiful

552
00:21:14,273 --> 00:21:17,026
than any jewels
in this world.

553
00:21:17,026 --> 00:21:18,986
That's right!

554
00:21:18,986 --> 00:21:20,696
That's just right!

555
00:21:20,696 --> 00:21:23,407
♪

556
00:21:23,407 --> 00:21:25,075
Happy wedding anniversary.

557
00:21:25,075 --> 00:21:28,913
She insisted on coming over
here to celebrate it with you.

558
00:21:28,913 --> 00:21:31,040
I see.

559
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:32,166
Thank you.

560
00:21:32,166 --> 00:21:34,835
But still,
I'm sorry that...

561
00:21:34,835 --> 00:21:36,879
I couldn't become a lady.

562
00:21:36,879 --> 00:21:38,088
I really am.

563
00:21:38,088 --> 00:21:39,882
(gong sounding)

564
00:21:39,882 --> 00:21:42,760
The road to becoming a...

565
00:21:42,760 --> 00:21:44,094
A lady!

566
00:21:44,094 --> 00:21:46,597
Someone who never
compromises her beliefs.

567
00:21:46,597 --> 00:21:48,349
Someone who can be
proud of all the things

568
00:21:48,349 --> 00:21:49,642
she really likes.

569
00:21:49,642 --> 00:21:52,937
Someone who is able to shine
without wearing a dress

570
00:21:52,937 --> 00:21:54,814
or any makeup.

571
00:21:54,814 --> 00:21:56,899
That is a lady!

572
00:21:56,899 --> 00:21:58,776
We're proud of you, Sunako.

573
00:21:58,776 --> 00:22:00,528
You're a respectable lady.

574
00:22:00,528 --> 00:22:03,155
Oh my, this is
quite emotional.

575
00:22:03,155 --> 00:22:05,491
Well, you can go home now.

576
00:22:05,491 --> 00:22:07,785
Let's get down from here
while that noise is still

577
00:22:07,785 --> 00:22:09,954
going on inside.

578
00:22:09,954 --> 00:22:12,540
Uh‐huh.

579
00:22:12,540 --> 00:22:20,506
♪

580
00:22:20,506 --> 00:22:22,550
(gasping)

581
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:27,388
♪

582
00:22:27,388 --> 00:22:29,390
Hey, watch out!

583
00:22:29,390 --> 00:22:42,111
♪

584
00:22:42,111 --> 00:22:43,654
Oh, lovely!

585
00:22:43,654 --> 00:22:44,864
Yes, Lady Tamao.

586
00:22:44,864 --> 00:22:46,156
Of course she is.

587
00:22:46,156 --> 00:22:48,659
You have no idea how hard
Sunako worked for this.

588
00:22:48,659 --> 00:22:50,703
She never got
introduced at the party.

589
00:22:50,703 --> 00:22:52,162
That's all right.

590
00:22:52,162 --> 00:22:54,665
Because as it turns out,

591
00:22:54,665 --> 00:22:58,460
she got to say the most
important thing, right?

592
00:22:58,460 --> 00:23:01,255
(blood squelching)

593
00:23:01,255 --> 00:23:02,965
(group recoils)

594
00:23:02,965 --> 00:23:04,717
It's just no good, huh?

595
00:23:04,717 --> 00:23:06,635
That's just how
a girl should be!

596
00:23:06,635 --> 00:23:08,804
Sunako should become
a classic Japanese lady

597
00:23:08,804 --> 00:23:10,681
who's beautiful
both inside and out.

598
00:23:10,681 --> 00:23:13,851
Don't you agree, my dear
who's a star in heaven?

599
00:23:13,851 --> 00:23:15,686
This is pretty exciting.

600
00:23:15,686 --> 00:23:18,230
This isn't over yet,
it's a nightmare!

601
00:23:18,230 --> 00:23:20,024
‐Hey, let's leave.
‐Huh?

602
00:23:20,024 --> 00:23:20,900
Hold it.

603
00:23:20,900 --> 00:23:22,776
Now I want you all
to turn my Sunako

604
00:23:22,776 --> 00:23:23,986
into a superlady!

605
00:23:23,986 --> 00:23:26,780
‐Give us a break!
‐Give me a break too!

606
00:23:26,780 --> 00:23:28,032
Then pay the rent!

607
00:23:28,032 --> 00:23:29,950
We don't want to do that either!

608
00:23:29,950 --> 00:23:31,169
Me either!

609
00:23:31,911 --> 00:23:34,538
♪

610
00:23:34,538 --> 00:23:36,957
It looks like there's
still quite a long way to go

611
00:23:36,957 --> 00:23:38,626
on the road to womanhood.

612
00:23:38,626 --> 00:23:40,586
(chuckling)

